/-- **The slice structure-sheaf ring map `œà_r`** (blueprint `lem:slice_structureSheaf_hom`).  The
over-pullback (to the slice `Over U·µ¢`) of the structure-sheaf comparison `œÜ.inv.toRingCatSheafHom`.
