which `SheafOfModules.pullback œà_r` (Need #1 `hqc`) is built. -/
noncomputable def sliceStructureSheafHom : (X.ringCatSheaf.over Ui) ‚ü∂
    ((Over.post (X := Ui) (Opens.map œÜ.inv.base)).sheafPushforwardContinuous RingCat
